= inline element occupy only exactly the space that's needed for the content.
= inline element doesn't create a break line after or before the other element.
= inline element the width and height style property don't have effect.
= Also padding and margin are only applied horizontally(left and right).
  
        margin: 20px;
  
  = the margin will be top=bottom=0, and left=right=20px;
  
= You can also change the block level element by using css property:

        display: inline;

= inline has default element: 
  [=] a
  [=] img
  [=] strong
  [=] em
  [=] button
  [=] and so on.